Date: 16/10/2025
Author: Uttam Cadambi Padmanaban

This is used to create the bounding box to be used in conjunction with CfMesh.

The goal is to create a single hexahedral block and then only extract the top, bottom, inlet and outlet faces (refer to the pdf for instructions, also posted below for convenience).

surfaceMeshTriangulate -patches '(inlet outlet top bottom)' bb.stl

